data.description: Prime location in Clemmons! This open concept offers cathedral ceilings with plenty of natural light. Large main level primary bedroom, with space for a second living area or office. Second story bedroom and bathroom with large closet and additional attic space. Sunroom with sliding glass panels, adjoined by an outdoor deck — perfect for entertaining! Attached one car garage. NEW ROOF JULY 2023. Large lot tucked perfectly off a cul-de-sac entrance. Just minutes away from shopping, dining, highways, and medical facilities!
